#!CDarkGreen #!N  #!Rccpgrid Changing the 
Alignment of Interactors in the Control Panel #!N #!EC #!N #!N 
You can specify whether the interactors you place in the Control 
Panel automatically align on a grid pattern. To do this, select 
 #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Grid... #!EF from the  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Options #!EF pull-down menu. The 
 #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Grid #!EF dialog box appears; it works the same way 
as it does in the VPE (see  #!Lwindset,dxall353 h Customizing the VPE Window  #!EL  ). #!N #!N 
